name: one unchill gal
description: The Unchill Gal Token celebrates unapologetic passion, inspired by the meme “My Old Character.” She’s not here to stay cool or indifferent—she’s an unchill gal who highkey gives a fuck. This token is a badge of honor for those who care deeply, speak boldly, and reject mediocrity, reminding us that caring fiercely is a superpower, not a flaw. “my old character. part of her deal is she's an unchill gal that highkey gives a fuck”
